name: Cydelete
tagline: Uninstall Cydia applications via the SpringBoard.
body:
CyDelete
=========

CyDelete lets you uninstall Cydia applications directly from the SpringBoard just like normal AppStore applications. Just hold a SpringBoard icon down and tap on the X and the app will be uninstalled.


 ![CyDelete](http://moreinfo.thebigboss.org/moreinfo/cydelete7-1.jpg).
 ![CyDelete](http://moreinfo.thebigboss.org/moreinfo/cydelete7-2.jpg).
